l banks be able to sustain the business in India given the highly regulated environment as compared to the overseas market where private banking literally translates into border less banking? Is there a future for online private banking, especially in the
 Indian context?
\par 
\par Finally, with banks increasingly garnering revenues from the \lquote niche\rquote  private banking services, what does this mean for the banking promise to touch every individual\rquote s life?
